e":"2017-09-10T11:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b627e8fac6bdc8cd8e226553fa523444e429e3a9","tid":394932,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170910/s00001/2a8ee772fdbaeb02941aae48557e2ad4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170910%2Fs00001%2F2a8ee772fdbaeb02941aae48557e2ad4.jpg&h=6263cf03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acc46cdfe7de160653699a2e85ef323482c3da96","tid":394932,"uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:41:50.000Z","msg":"2017-09-10<br />\n<br />\n葵涌邨驚現疑似胎盤！一名保安於逸葵樓近變壓房位置發現一個懷疑胎盤物體，警方接報到場登樓調查，並派出大批動部隊人員到附近一帶搜索，惟至今未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n事發在早上8時許，保安途經逸葵樓近變壓房位置時，發現地上滿佈血迹，附近有大堆雜物及黑膠袋，感到可疑遂報警求助。警方接報到場調查，在膠袋內發現染血毛巾，經搜索後在現場附近發現疑似胎盤的物體，但未有發現任何屍體。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後派出機動部隊人員登樓調查，並在附近一帶搜索，惟並無發現。案件列作「求警調查」處理，交由荃灣刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n至下午3時許，警方加大搜查範圍到附近公園及山頭調查，並出動警犬到場協助，葵青警區重案組探員其後亦有到場調查。"},{"pid":"2dc50e55b03cc28fc13b140e3652873d5a2bb0a3","tid":394932,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:42:52.000Z","msg":"Cls<br />\n係咪拎左個b去餵野狗"},{"pid":"7e10daff04dd3adb8c6278805eb797bc2f8f9384","tid":394932,"uid":131526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bc504b99eede084b8249b5113de726741acf1d","tid":394932,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d93b70402254e9dcdaca794b4d5f454a920b968","tid":394932,"uid":10894,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e078796ead5678d24f2d94187e24d6f634726d29","tid":39